------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Output & data handling
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This repository ships SOURCE CODE, not model outputs. Operators supply their own API
keys and are responsible for complying with each provider's Terms of Service and
Acceptable Use Policy.

The only model outputs committed to this repository are example briefs under
examples/, generated exclusively with the open / Nebius-hosted models named above
(Llama 3.3, Gemma 3), whose terms permit such use.

This tool does NOT collect, retain, or use model outputs to train, fine-tune,
distill, or develop any AI model. Doing so is prohibited by most providers' terms;
operators must not repurpose this template for that.
